## Getting Started

```bash
# Build all crates
cargo build --workspace

# Run tests
cargo test --workspace

# Check all
cargo check --workspace
```

## Architecture

This workspace follows a clean separation of concerns:

- **core** — Domain logic, shared types, error definitions
- **cli** — Command-line interface, user-facing commands
- **utils** — Shared utilities, helpers, formatting

